#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:17
msgid ""
"Create an employee by going to :menuselection:`Employees --> New`. Go to "
"the :guilabel:`Settings` tab, and configure the :guilabel:`Australian "
